body_html:
I can't think of recent api generation changes that could cause it. Api generation should not impact custom ops.

@christiantinauer What is the name of the op that doesn't load? I see tf.extract_volume_patches in 1.12 but not in 1.11:
https://www.tensorflow.org/api_docs/python/tf/extract_volume_patches

Could there be a possible name conflict:
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/python/framework/load_library.py#L47

edit: fixed typo
